title: Life After ‘Bachelorette’ with Garrett & Bryan
description:
Garrett Yrigoyen and Bryan Abasolo are back in the studio for another double date. Rachel, Becca, Bryan and Garrett talk about life after the show and what it was like starting their lives off camera.

Plus, the couples reveal the biggest misconceptions that people tend to have about them and their lives post-show.

Be sure to rate and subscribe so you never miss an episode.
